                <expan><abbr>Cn</abbr><ex>aei</ex></expan> Allei Nigidi <lb n="2"/>Mai <expan><abbr>quinq</abbr><ex>uennalis</ex></expan> sine impensa publica <expan><abbr>glad</abbr><ex>iatorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>par</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> XX et eorum <expan><abbr>supp</abbr><ex>ositicii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pugn</abbr><ex>abunt</ex></expan> Pompeis </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Gavellius Tigillo <lb n="2"/>et Clodio <expan><abbr>sal</abbr><ex>utem</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Telephe summa rudis <lb n="4"/>instrumentum muneris <lb n="5"/>u<expan><ex>b</ex><abbr>i</abbr><ex>que</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>va</abbr><ex>le</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Diadumeno et Pyladioni
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Am Ende der 6. Zeile des zweiten Teils der Inschrift ein einem L ähnliches Zeichen, das Della Corte als `compendio della parola feliciter&amp;apos; auffaßt.</p>
